{"tid":1963361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛強烈譴責在非洲進行人體疫苗試驗言論","createTime":"2020-04-08T05:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T13:38:04.000Z","uid":125168,"like":151,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"34dfe04bf44b2c34b6d3520e35a5a3ea3f278c83","tid":1963361,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"世衛強烈譴責在非洲進行人體疫苗試驗言論<br />\n4分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】法國有醫生提議在非洲進行新冠病毒疫苗人體測試，引來外界猛烈抨擊。世衛予以最強烈譴責，形容在21世紀還聽到這種言論是恥辱。<br />\n<br />\n法國駐南非大使館對事件表示震驚，強調相關言論絕不代表法國當局的立場。<br />\n<br />\n接受法國電視台訪問時發表人體疫苗試驗言論的兩名醫生，分別是巴黎科尚醫院的米拉，以及法國國家衛生研究院研究部門主管洛赫特，他們已就事件致歉。<br />\n<br />\n非洲多個團體也表示強烈反對，目前非洲累計約有一萬宗確診個案，四百多人死亡。54個非洲國家中，只有2個未有病例，多國已採取封城措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=387154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387154&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=9cb696b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387154&h=db7e925d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=387154</a>"},{"pid":"e30d2058dadb640b381fdb899a2a1f18d4504fd2","tid":1963361,"uid":177168,"like":101,"dislike":47,"score":54,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"非洲人是命賤架啦"},{"pid":"5f0f4ec0426fb2a4e52a2f59a46c01f8aa68b919","tid":1963361,"uid":42751,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"唔通搵歐洲人去試咩"},{"pid":"837447a13ff818ed12273363a525e97aca270536","tid":1963361,"uid":10637,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"WHO fuck off la"},{"pid":"b0d8156031e50c2370aa0c5d0ac0da0fe64d2ecc","tid":1963361,"uid":45518,"like":239,"dislike":0,"score":239,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"搵中国人試囉"},{"pid":"872afb06f1135f06f65fc5344a5df6e52c0042d9"